@{
}
<style>

    .jumbotron {
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        background: #2F3136;
        height: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    #ButtonDT {
        position: relative;
        height: 40px;
        align-content: center;
        line-height: 30px;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #53538C;
        font-size: 25px;
        left: 17%;
        width: 70%;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        border-radius: 25px;
    }
    .card {
        background: #2F3136;
        border-block-color: #2F3136;
        border-inline-color: #2F3136;
        min-height: calc(100% - 15px);
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        height: 200px;
    }
    .col-sm {
        height: calc(100% - 100px);
        margin-bottom: 1px;
    }

    h3 {
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 1px;
    }

    .btn-success {
        border-radius: 25px;
        background-color: #575777;
        border-color: #575777;
        margin-top: 5px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .row {
        min-height: calc(100% - 15px);
        margin-bottom: 1px;
    }
    .h1{
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
</style>
<a>@ViewBag.message</a>

<h1> Dashboard </h1>



<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm">
        <div class="jumbotron">

            <h3> Servers </h3>

            <div class="col-sm">
                <div class="card card-body row-match-height">
                    <p>
                        "here you can pick a server you're an admin for and  add Box bot to it.
                        or pick which server bot you whant to edit."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a class="btn" id="ButtonDT" asp-area="" asp-controller="Authentication" asp-action="ServerList">Enter</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
        <div class="jumbotron">

            <h3> Settings </h3>

            <div class="col-sm ">
                <div class="card card-body row-match-height">
                    <p>
                        "Here you can edit, Box Bots settings,
                        for your Server. Add, Delete, Uppdate Words in your list of censored Word.
                        change Powerful your punishment are and when the trigger."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a class="btn" id="ButtonDT" asp-area="" asp-controller="Settings" asp-action="Settings">Enter</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
        <div class="jumbotron">

            <h3> Statistics </h3>

            <div class="col-sm ">
                <div class="card card-body row-match-height">
                    <p>
                        "Here You can see an overview of box bots, influence on your server through statistics"
                    </p>
                </div>
                <a class="btn" id="ButtonDT" asp-area="" asp-controller="Authentication" asp-action="Authentication">Enter</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

